    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition vehicle that runs and drives well and presents nicely overall. The body and paint show normal signs of age and use, but nothing out of line for a vehicle in this condition, and the interior is clean, comfortable, and well cared for. It\u2019s not perfect or like-new, but it has clearly been maintained and should make a solid, dependable choice for someone looking for a nice driver without paying top-of-market money.",
