    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer seeking low-cost transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows clear cosmetic and mechanical wear consistent with its age, but it offers real value for someone who wants an inexpensive entry point without unnecessary hype. Priced to sell and ideal for a handy owner, commuter on a budget, or anyone needing basic wheels at a sensible price.",
