      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s got plenty of life left for the right buyer. A great option for someone handy, needing cheap transportation, or wanting a fixer-upper without spending a fortune. I like to be upfront: it shows its age and needs some love, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. If you want something honest, budget-friendly, and worth a look, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project or budget daily with solid bones and plenty of usable life left. The drivetrain pulls well, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of honest, mechanical character enthusiasts appreciate. Not a showroom car, but a great opportunity for someone who wants dependable transportation, a weekend wrenching project, or an affordable platform to sort and improve. Priced to move and well worth a look.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
